text: Izatullah Dawlatzai was born 10 May, 1991 in Nangarhar Province, Afghanistan. He is an Afghan-German cricketer who played 5 one-day internationals and 16 Twenty20 Internationals for Afghanistan and Germany. ==Other websites== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Afghan cricketers Category:German cricketers Category:21st-century Afghan people
title: Izatullah Dawlatzai
